name: Rocky Mountain High
description: Rocky Mountain High is an indica-dominant hybrid from Colorado that crosses Mikado with Colorado Green Bud. This strain was originally bred by Hazeman Seeds, who recommends a 63 day flowering time for this indica when grown indoors.
attributes_title: Euphoric, Creative, Focused, Uplifted, Relaxed, Pain, Nausea, Stress, Depression, Fatigue, Paranoid, Anxious, Dry Mouth, Dizzy, Dry Eyes
